      "updated": 1703000001008,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Access + route parameters\n\n- TEACHER JWT via require_role(UserRole.TEACHER)\n- course_id on every route\n- student_id for /student/{student_id}/portfolio and /twin\n- POST bodies:\n  WhatIfRequest\n  SkillSimulationRequest\n  MultiSkillSimulationRequest\n- Neo4j must be configured, else HTTP 503",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Access + route parameters\n\n- TEACHER JWT via require_role(UserRole.TEACHER)\n- course_id on every route\n- student_id for /student/{student_id}/portfolio and /twin\n- POST bodies:\n  WhatIfRequest\n  SkillSimulationRequest\n  MultiSkillSimulationRequest\n- Neo4j must be configured, else HTTP 503",
      "lineHeight": 1.2
    },
