      "updated": 1703000001010,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Learning data pulled from Neo4j\n\n- STUDENT -> CLASS enrollments\n- STUDENT -> SKILL SELECTED_SKILL\n- STUDENT -> SKILL MASTERED\n  mastery, decay, status, attempt_count,\n  correct_count, updated_at_ts\n- STUDENT -> QUESTION ATTEMPTED\n  is_correct, timestamp_sec, time_spent_sec\n- STUDENT -> READING_RESOURCE or VIDEO_RESOURCE ENGAGES_WITH\n  progress, duration_sec, event_type, started_at\n- skill co-selection sets per course",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Learning data pulled from Neo4j\n\n- STUDENT -> CLASS enrollments\n- STUDENT -> SKILL SELECTED_SKILL\n- STUDENT -> SKILL MASTERED\n  mastery, decay, status, attempt_count,\n  correct_count, updated_at_ts\n- STUDENT -> QUESTION ATTEMPTED\n  is_correct, timestamp_sec, time_spent_sec\n- STUDENT -> READING_RESOURCE or VIDEO_RESOURCE ENGAGES_WITH\n  progress, duration_sec, event_type, started_at\n- skill co-selection sets per course",
      "lineHeight": 1.2
    },
