      "updated": 1703000001014,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Authorization / guard rails / optional services\n\n- teacher_teaches_class(teacher_id, course_id)\n  enforced before student portfolio/twin drilldown\n- HTTP 403 if teacher does not teach the class\n- Optional LLM narratives:\n  WhatIfRequest.enable_llm -> llm_recommendation\n  multi-skill automatic or multi-skill manual -> llm_insights\n- LLM uses OpenAI-compatible base_url + model settings",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Authorization / guard rails / optional services\n\n- teacher_teaches_class(teacher_id, course_id)\n  enforced before student portfolio/twin drilldown\n- HTTP 403 if teacher does not teach the class\n- Optional LLM narratives:\n  WhatIfRequest.enable_llm -> llm_recommendation\n  multi-skill automatic or multi-skill manual -> llm_insights\n- LLM uses OpenAI-compatible base_url + model settings",
      "lineHeight": 1.2
    },
