      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Skill Difficulty  GET /skill-difficulty\nFormula: AvgMastery(s) = mean student mastery for skill s\nPerceivedDifficulty(s) = 1 - AvgMastery(s)\nReturns per-skill student_count, avg_mastery, perceived_difficulty, total_skills",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Skill Difficulty  GET /skill-difficulty\nFormula: AvgMastery(s) = mean student mastery for skill s\nPerceivedDifficulty(s) = 1 - AvgMastery(s)\nReturns per-skill student_count, avg_mastery, perceived_difficulty, total_skills",
      "lineHeight": 1.2
    },
