      "versionNonce": 5029,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1703000001029,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5. What-If  POST /what-if\nManual mode: teacher provides skills + hypothetical_mastery\nAutomatic mode: apply delta boost across skills\nClassGain(skill) = sum(min(1, mastery + delta) - mastery)\nOutputs simulated_path, pco_analysis, recommendations, skill_impacts,\nsummary, and optional llm_recommendation",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5. What-If  POST /what-if\nManual mode: teacher provides skills + hypothetical_mastery\nAutomatic mode: apply delta boost across skills\nClassGain(skill) = sum(min(1, mastery + delta) - mastery)\nOutputs simulated_path, pco_analysis, recommendations, skill_impacts,\nsummary, and optional llm_recommendation",
      "lineHeight": 1.2
    },
