      "updated": 1703000001031,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "6. Skill Simulation + Multi-Skill Simulation\nPOST /simulate-skill -> one adaptive exercise for one skill at simulated_mastery\nPOST /simulate-skills -> many adaptive exercises + coherence analysis\nAutomatic multi-skill mode auto-selects hardest skills by lowest avg_mastery\nCoherence uses pairwise Jaccard + clusters where Jaccard >= 0.40",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "6. Skill Simulation + Multi-Skill Simulation\nPOST /simulate-skill -> one adaptive exercise for one skill at simulated_mastery\nPOST /simulate-skills -> many adaptive exercises + coherence analysis\nAutomatic multi-skill mode auto-selects hardest skills by lowest avg_mastery\nCoherence uses pairwise Jaccard + clusters where Jaccard >= 0.40",
      "lineHeight": 1.2
    },
