      "originalText": "Grouping + simulation responses\n\nStudentGroupsResponse\n- course_id, groups[StudentGroup], ungrouped_students, total_groups\n\nWhatIfResponse\n- mode, course_id, simulated_path, pco_analysis,\n  recommendations, skill_impacts, summary, llm_recommendation?\n\nSkillSimulationResponse\n- skill_name, simulated_mastery, perceived_difficulty,\n  avg_class_mastery, student_count,\n  question, options, correct_index, explanation\n\nMultiSkillSimulationResponse\n- mode, course_id, auto_selected_skills,\n  skill_results[SkillSimResult], coherence, llm_insights?",
