      "text": "Teacher drilldown proxy outputs\n\nPortfolio endpoint returns dict built from ArcdPortfolioData\n- generated_at\n- datasets[{id, name, model_info, skills, students[]}]\n\nTwin endpoint returns ArcdTwinViewerData\n- student_id, generated_at, dataset\n- current_twin\n- snapshot_history\n- risk_forecast\n- scenario_comparison\n- twin_confidence\n- recommended_schedule_summary",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Teacher drilldown proxy outputs\n\nPortfolio endpoint returns dict built from ArcdPortfolioData\n- generated_at\n- datasets[{id, name, model_info, skills, students[]}]\n\nTwin endpoint returns ArcdTwinViewerData\n- student_id, generated_at, dataset\n- current_twin\n- snapshot_history\n- risk_forecast\n- scenario_comparison\n- twin_confidence\n- recommended_schedule_summary",
      "lineHeight": 1.2
