    {
      "id": "ttd_schema_text1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 56,
      "y": 1036,
      "width": 468,
      "height": 298,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#0f172a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 5051,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 5051,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1703000001051,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Neo4j node labels\n\nUSER:STUDENT\n- id\n\nUSER:TEACHER\n- id\n\nCLASS\n- id\n\nSKILL / BOOK_SKILL / MARKET_SKILL\n- name\n\nQUESTION\n- id\n\nREADING_RESOURCE\n- id\n\nVIDEO_RESOURCE\n- id\n\nTeacher Digital Twin primarily reads the graph projection.\nSQL is mainly used earlier for auth / course identity,\nbut this module's analytics path is graph-centric.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Neo4j node labels\n\nUSER:STUDENT\n- id\n\nUSER:TEACHER\n- id\n\nCLASS\n- id\n\nSKILL / BOOK_SKILL / MARKET_SKILL\n- name\n\nQUESTION\n- id\n\nREADING_RESOURCE\n- id\n\nVIDEO_RESOURCE\n- id\n\nTeacher Digital Twin primarily reads the graph projection.\nSQL is mainly used earlier for auth / course identity,\nbut this module's analytics path is graph-centric.",
      "lineHeight": 1.2
    },
    {
      "id": "ttd_schema_box2",
